<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>
<simplesect><title>template&lt;typename T&gt;<?linebreak?>class KTN::Core::SPSCRingBuffer&lt; T &gt;</title></simplesect>

<para>A single-producer, single-consumer ring buffer implementation. </para>



<para>This class provides a thread-safe ring buffer that can be used in a single-producer, single-consumer scenario. It supports enqueueing and dequeueing elements, as well as checking the size and emptiness of the buffer.</para>

